    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>chives </strong>finely</p><p>Dice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p>",
