    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>diced tomato</strong> to the <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>dressing</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p>",
