      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>herby mushrooms</strong> over the <strong>creamy roasted garlic tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and<strong> remaining grated cheese</strong> and serve the<strong> balsamic salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
